# File Structure Map — Solo Developer Edition

## Monorepo Root
```
co-op/                          ← Turborepo monorepo root
├── apps/web/                   ← Next.js 15 frontend
├── services/api/               ← FastAPI backend (COMPLETE ✅)
├── services/communication/     ← Stage 3: Telegram + Email service
├── infrastructure/docker/      ← Docker Compose config
├── packages/                   ← Shared packages (empty Stage 1)
├── docs/                       ← Architecture docs + stage guides
│   ├── rules/                  ← AI IDE constraint files (.mdc)
│   ├── CO_OP_SOLO_DEVELOPER_ARCHITECTURE.md
│   ├── CO_OP_SOLO_TASKS_UPDATED.md
│   ├── stage1_implementation.md
│   ├── stage2_implementation.md
│   ├── stage3_implementation.md
│   └── stage4_implementation.md
├── turbo.json
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml
├── package.json
├── .env                        ← Root env (sync with docker/.env)
└── .env.example
```

