├── worker.py                   ← Stage 2: ARQ WorkerSettings + cron jobs
│
├── routers/
│   ├── auth.py                 ← POST /v1/auth/token, refresh, me
│   ├── chat.py                 ← POST /v1/chat/stream (SSE)
