## Infrastructure
```
infrastructure/docker/
├── docker-compose.yml          ← Services (grows per stage)
├── .env                        ← Secrets (Stage 1-2: here, Stage 3+: Vault)
├── litellm_config.yaml         ← Stage 2: LLM model routing
└── supervisord.conf            ← Stage 2: Run uvicorn + arq in one container
```

